#NMFire burn scar flooding update:

The communities of Cañoncito, Manuelita, Sapello, Gascon, Rociada, Lower Rociada, and Las Dispensas have been advised to evacuate to a safe place away from possible flood and debris flow areas.

@NMStatePolice and @NMDOT are on scene assisting.

In the last year, we:
🌎Implemented rules that require 98% gas capture by 2026 in the oil and gas sector; 
🌿Enacted an Executive Order to conserve 30% of  lands by 2030; 
☀️Doubled the number of renewable energy leases on state trust lands; 
🚗Adopted clean car rules

